        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Exogenous VGF peptides acutely enhance synaptic activity.\n\n30/4/2018 Pim\n- The authors show that BDNF-increases the expression of immediate Early Gene and of the VGF peptide. The VGF peptide is shown to modulate synaptic transmission when applied in culture.. Experimental description: \"Low-density cultures of dissociated embryonic day 18 rat hippocampi (Sprague Dawley) ...\" p. 10801" ;
